  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA Generic Centrifugal Pump Hemolysis Credibility Assessment (Fully Assessed, Accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative hemolysis trends for a Class II blood pump at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for each factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision: Accepted.",
